data.description: New Year...New price...New you! Welcome home to Westchester Place!  It feels like home the moment you step into the foyer.  Elegantly refreshed, this one-bedroom plus loft offers a cozy retreat. The loft which features a half bath and an ample sized closet, provides the flexibility of a family area or den as well as the opportunity to be converted to a master suite!  This freshly redone interior exudes charm and functionality and with the well-appointed laundry closet and separate utility closet, you'll have convenience at your fingertips. You'll also enjoy the outdoors on the concrete patio right outside of the eating area.  You can conveniently park in the attached one-car garage and enter your unit blending comfort and practicality seamlessly.
